1、对整个wiki生效：打开 [[$:/ControlPanel]] ，在外观-主题调整-设置-字型文本框内，最前面添加 `"屏显臻宋",`；

2、对单个条目生效：添加字段 `font`，字段内容 `ZS`。"},"屏显臻宋.woff2":{"title":"屏显臻宋.woff2","text":"","type":"application/octet-stream","created":"20250508033911300","modified":"20250508033926593"},"引用字体-屏显臻宋":{"title":"引用字体-屏显臻宋","code-body":"yes","created":"20250508033811012","modified":"20250508033825698","tags":"字体","text":"@font-face {
	font-family: "屏显臻宋";
	font-style: normal;
	font-weight: 400;
	src: local("屏显臻宋"), url(<<datauri "屏显臻宋.woff2">>) format("woff2");
}
"},"按字段font=ZS引用字体-屏显臻宋":{"title":"按字段font=ZS引用字体-屏显臻宋","code-body":"yes","created":"20250508033829841","modified":"20250508033842229","tags":"字体 $:/tags/Stylesheet","text":"<$list filter="[font[ZS]]">

}
</$list>"}}}
